"text": "($40) million", "bbox": [822.3, 635.2, 928.2, 655.2]}, {"text": "2008 vs. 2007 –", "bbox": [90.5, 681.1, 244.1, 701.7]}, {"text": "● Sales and Operating Income – Operating results were impacted positively by lower average live prices and strong export", "bbox": [90.5, 704.2, 1128.3, 724.3]}, {"text": "sales, which led to increased sales volume and a record year for operating margins. Fiscal 2008 operating results include", "bbox": [142.8, 727.2, 1110.2, 747.1]}, {"text": "realized and unrealized net gains of $95 million from our commodity risk management activities related to forward futures", "bbox": [142.8, 750.3, 1128.6, 770.2]}, {"text": "contracts for live hogs, excluding the related impact from the physical sale and purchase transactions, compared to realized", "bbox": [142.8, 773.3, 1132.4, 793.2]}, {"text": "and unrealized net gains of $3 million recorded in fiscal 2007. This was partially offset by higher operating costs, as well as", "bbox": [142.8, 796.2, 1137.7, 816.1]}, {"text": "lower average sales prices.", "bbox": [142.8, 819.2, 362.3, 839.1]}, {"text": "Prepared Foods Segment Results", "bbox": [90.5, 865.8, 377.2, 885.9]}, {"text": "in millions", "bbox": [967.2, 865.3, 1063.4, 885.2]}, {"text": "2009", "bbox": [477.7, 915.3, 527.6, 935.2]}, {"text": "2008", "bbox": [592.9, 915.3, 663.3, 935.2]}, {"text": "Change 2009", "bbox": [670.1, 892.2, 781.3, 912.1]}, {"text": "vs. 2008", "bbox": [708.7, 915.3, 786.5, 935.2]}, {"text": "2007", "bbox": [864.3, 915.3, 914.5, 935.2]}, {"text": "Change 2008", "bbox": [947.0, 892.2, 1058.2, 912.1]}, {"text": "vs. 2007", "bbox": [985.7, 915.3, 1063.4, 935.2]}, {"text": "Sales", "bbox": [90.5, 942.4, 137.7, 962.3]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [428.9, 942.4, 443.9, 962.3]}, {"text": "2,836", "bbox": [472.6, 942.4, 527.6, 962.3]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [544.2, 942.4, 559.2, 962.3]}, {"text": "2,711   $", "bbox": [587.9, 942.4, 673.1, 962.3]}, {"text": "125", "bbox": [746.4, 942.4, 786.5, 962.3]}, {"text": "$", "bbo