0.5, 1222.4, 244.1, 1243.0]}, {"text": "● Sales and Operating Income – Operating results improved due to an increase in sales volume, as well as a reduction in", "bbox": [90.5, 1245.5, 1109.1, 1266.1]}, {"text": "raw material costs that exceeded the decrease in our average sales prices. In addition, we made several operational", "bbox": [142.8, 1268.5, 1061.7, 1288.4]}, {"text": "improvements in fiscal 2009 that allow us to run our plants more efficiently. We began realizing the majority of these", "bbox": [142.8, 1291.6, 1088.1, 1311.5]}, {"text": "improvements in our operating results during the latter part of fiscal 2009.", "bbox": [142.8, 1314.6, 741.3, 1334.5]}, {"text": "2008 vs. 2007 –", "bbox": [90.5, 1360.5, 244.1, 1381.1]}, {"text": "● Sales and Operating Income – Operating results were negatively impacted by higher raw material costs, which include", "bbox": [90.5, 1383.5, 1111.5, 1404.1]}, {"text": "wheat, dairy and cooking ingredient costs, partially offset by lower pork costs. Results were positively impacted by an", "bbox": [142.8, 1406.6, 1093.5, 1426.5]}, {"text": "increase in average sales prices.", "bbox": [142.8, 1429.7, 403.0, 1449.6]}]}